  "body": "Since codemirror doesn't understand JSX properly, the editors on the website behave strangely with indentation sometime. I'd like to create a full-blown JSX mode, but until then, I think we can disable the \"smart\" indentation behavior.\n\nI think we want to turn off `smartIndent` and `electricChars`:\n\nhttp://codemirror.net/doc/manual.html\n",
